Asia‑Pacific – Rapid expansion driven by urbanisation, rising disposable income, and government initiatives that upgrade surgical suites. Growing demand for both straight and curved clip designs across the region.
Latin America – Increasing surgical activity and healthcare investment create opportunities for both premium and cost‑effective clip solutions.
Middle East and Africa – Emerging market with early adopters in Gulf countries; focus on durable, cost‑effective designs for broader adoption.
